## 11. Key Architectural Decisions & Why
| Decision | Rationale |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Sequential over Hierarchical** | Deterministic, avoids 429 errors on NIM free tier, no manager LLM overhead. |
| **`max_rpm=10`** | Optimized balance between throughput and rate-limiting. |
| **`Any` type on `get_background_knowledge`** | Prevents Pydantic v2 validation crashes when CrewAI passes structured objects. |
| **15-review limit + 500 char truncation** | Prevents `ContextWindowExceeded` crashes on high-activity users like "Carlos". |
| **`friends` field removal** | Strips 500KB+ of useless data to save context and speed up inference. |
| **4-layer JSON sanitizer** | Handles markdown wrapping, explanation text, and `{{` escaping in LLM output. |
| **YAML-first configuration** | Complies with `crewai-strict-separation.md` rule for role/task isolation. |
| **`time.sleep(30)` in agent** | Mandatory inter-task cooling to prevent 429 rate limit violations. |

---

